{"tid":1068814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭人　跳毛利戰舞　向基督城　穆斯林死者　致哀","createTime":"2019-03-19T13:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T14:11:58.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a215f1b5c15ac6572bc5d1c73bba6d5b352d43ef","tid":1068814,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9NiNfjd67JU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9NiNfjd67JU&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=62527eeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9NiNfjd67JU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/26175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F26175&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=2af11805\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/26175</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lt6GRghrmaU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dlt6GRghrmaU&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=a1090570\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lt6GRghrmaU</a><br />\n<br />\n一位老師要退休離開學校了，而這次北帕莫斯頓男子高中（Palmerston North Boys' High School）學生歡送他的方式，是一起跳毛利戰舞（HAKA）！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F40154&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=04c3ab1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/40154</a><br />\n<br />\n最近紐西蘭網友瘋傳一支令人心碎的影片。影片中，一位17歲男孩的葬禮上，朋友們跳起毛利戰舞「哈卡」（HAKA）為他送別。領舞男孩情緒幾近潰堤，但他哽咽強忍淚水、堅持跳完這支舞，送朋友最後一程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3732/3732864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3732%2F3732864.jpg&h=320e3598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／Anthony Hall）<br />\n<br />\n17歲的Jarom Rihari自殺身亡，朋友們感到錯愕、不捨。當他的靈車開離教堂時，一群青少年克制悲痛的情緒，列陣跳起「哈卡舞」，大聲呼喊、頓足、槌胸，氣勢磅礡而悲壯，這是他們對朋友最後、最高的敬意。<br />\n<br />\n「哈卡舞」是紐西蘭原住民毛利人的傳統舞蹈，在婚喪喜慶特殊場合經常出現，許多運動員甚至會在比賽前跳上一段「哈卡」，展現輸人不輸陣的氣勢。哈卡包含許多意思，像是戰爭中的勇猛士氣，還有對客人的歡迎，以及在各種場合舉辦的相聚儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=blYY3H17Tlg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DblYY3H17Tlg&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=0f22c403\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=blYY3H17Tlg</a>"},{"pid":"044be8e4cdca66ad625c61103cac0ac8dc1c7c58","tid":1068814,"uid":149342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"中國人可以跳蘭陵王入陣曲"},{"pid":"c74a324d42581ec18ae89ecf9cf7fc98a8614ca6","tid":1068814,"uid":134202,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"點解冇穆斯林跳既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8565ab60299543089c8cd32729a677b315749d11","tid":1068814,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"毛利元就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff7bf269dfd8c2bc0878f35089dcf7da3fa47c5","tid":1068814,"uid":132038,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b182be2f5b449d72442a109863dd40bfb2af70ef","tid":1068814,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"跳黎向穆斯林宣戰就差唔多"},{"pid":"566f1d88a3fe48d4749e72e2307e052b280124e7","tid":1068814,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"第幾段片係向穆斯林致哀？"},{"pid":"67a847379a5e6e974124e7cc99e2edd41f58f838","tid":1068814,"uid":353,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RpoUNqZ.png\" data-thumbnai